task_details.mathematical_formulation:
Dynamic model of quadrotor UAV in the inertial frame:

m\ddot{x} = (\cos\phi\sin\theta\cos\psi + \sin\phi\sin\psi)u_1 + F_{wind,x} - F_{drag,x}
m\ddot{y} = (\cos\phi\sin\theta\sin\psi - \sin\phi\cos\psi)u_1 + F_{wind,y} - F_{drag,y}
m\ddot{z} = -mg + (\cos\phi\cos\theta)u_1 + F_{wind,z} - F_{drag,z}
I_x\ddot{\phi} = \dot{\theta}\dot{\psi}(I_y - I_z) + u_2 + M_{wind,x}
I_y\ddot{\theta} = \dot{\phi}\dot{\psi}(I_z - I_x) + u_3 + M_{wind,y}
I_z\ddot{\psi} = \dot{\phi}\dot{\theta}(I_x - I_y) + u_4 + M_{wind,z}

Where control inputs relate to rotor speeds:
u_1 = b(\omega_1^2 + \omega_2^2 + \omega_3^2 + \omega_4^2)
u_2 = lb(\omega_4^2 - \omega_2^2)
u_3 = lb(\omega_3^2 - \omega_1^2)
u_4 = d(\omega_1^2 - \omega_2^2 + \omega_3^2 - \omega_4^2)

Duffs model for wind disturbance:
F_{wind} = \frac{1}{2}\rho A C_d |v_{wind} - v_{uav}|(v_{wind} - v_{uav})

Optimal control problem formulation:
Minimize J = \int_{t_0}^{t_f} (\sum_{i=1}^{4} c_1\omega_i^2 + c_2||e_{pos}||^2 + c_3||e_{att}||^2 + c_4u_{smooth})dt

Lyapunov stability analysis for the proposed controller:
V(x) = \frac{1}{2}e^T P e
\dot{V}(x) = e^T P \dot{e} = e^T P (Ae + B\delta)
For stability: \dot{V}(x) < 0 \forall x \neq 0
